item.title: OpenStreetMap
item.description: OpenStreetMap makes it easy to create a beautiful map for free using QGIS. Customize anything on your map with widgets, themes, and language packs. Introduction Learn OSM Download OpenStreetMap data for this region: You can help. Map any place in the world even if you’ve never been there. Why would you use OpenStreetMap if there is Google Maps? Overpass API Manual custom geocoding using OSM database Near real-time OpenStreetMap editing.
